* Möbius seam = compression, indecision, balance point
* ZPC gate = only enter when resolution points your way
* stored gain = conviction, capital, positioning
* feed-forward = pyramiding only when the move confirms

Translation:
Don’t trade every wiggle.
Only capture motion when the market is near decision and resolving in your favor.

